    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《林夜终告》</strong>是一款黑暗恐怖游戏，你将扮演一名国家公园的夜班护林员。查看监控摄像头画面时，你开始注意到种种诡异事件。深入调查，揭开绿荫森林国家公园背后触目惊心的秘密。窗户那边好像有动静？别担心，只是又一只鹿而已。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>审核相机照片报告</strong>——作为夜班护林员，检查相机报告是你的职责所在。但问题是，有些照片……不太对劲？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209480/extras/0bdfc42dfa1b73f0fc862e17ecd32649.poster.avif?t=1764260150\" width=578 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209480/extras/0bdfc42dfa1b73f0fc862e17ecd32649.webm?t=1764260150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209480/extras/0bdfc42dfa1b73f0fc862e17ecd32649.mp4?t=1764260150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>体验绿荫森林公园的黑暗恐怖历史</strong>——你须揭开公园内隐藏的神秘过往……你可曾看见森林里流窜的身影？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209480/extras/13bffd761e887dac5aec74eda926b99e.poster.avif?t=1764260150\" width=578 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209480/extras/13bffd761e887dac5aec74eda926b99e.webm?t=1764260150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209480/extras/13bffd761e887dac5aec74eda926b99e.mp4?t=1764260150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与护林员同事对话</strong>——与其他护林员交谈互动，了解他们，并在最危急的时刻做出关键抉择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209480/extras/ef48c027a13a76d0089d409021efc4bd.poster.avif?t=1764260150\" width=578 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209480/extras/ef48c027a13a76d0089d409021efc4bd.webm?t=1764260150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209480/extras/ef48c027a13a76d0089d409021efc4bd.mp4?t=1764260150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑暗神秘的气氛</strong>——周围的自然环境可能暗藏危险，尤其是夜幕降临后，你很容易迷失在重重树影之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209480/extras/40bd007ac80b375c70bdff7fbdd0c156.poster.avif?t=1764260150\" width=578 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209480/extras/40bd007ac80b375c70bdff7fbdd0c156.webm?t=1764260150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209480/extras/40bd007ac80b375c70bdff7fbdd0c156.mp4?t=1764260150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >审核照片报告</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开绿荫森林公园的黑暗恐怖历史</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >担任夜班护林员</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与护林员同事对话互动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在至暗时刻做出关键抉择</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑暗神秘的气氛</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
